{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey where destiny and choices intertwine. <i>Amara: Demon Will</i> is a captivating pixel action game that blends an emotional narrative with immersive exploration.<br>Play as Amara, a white-haired girl, traveling through a mystical world filled with enigmas. Engage in combat with swift dodges, unleash powerful skills, and unravel the secrets hidden in ancient ruins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every choice you make shapes your future:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Combat and Strategy</strong>: Defeat formidable enemies through a fluid combat system and dynamic skill combinations.</u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Emotion and Decisions</strong>: Face inner struggles and make choices with profound consequences on an unpredictable journey.</u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Pixel Art and Atmosphere</strong>: Discover a fantastical world brought to life with intricate pixel art and an evocative original soundtrack.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you evade the darkness or confront it? Will you succumb or rise above? Your story is yours to tell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975290/extras/\u5fae\u4fe1\u56fe\u7247_20241126114555.png?t=1732763143\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732763143","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975290/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732763143","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975290/414a8dae8bfc2f74e5d1af51911628c5c2a5146f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732763143","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset